         <abstract id="aspace_2274eb26804e8ec189018766c7211c7e">Correspondence, memoranda, reports and miscellanea of Charles A. Russell. Professional material from public welfare, education, and international cultural cooperative organizations including the Edward W. Hazen Foundation are present.</abstract>
